  "body": "Fixes an issue where if a component throws, its instance variables are not reset before `componentWillUnmount` is called. See https://jsfiddle.net/m3pL3yaj/ for an illustration.\r\n\r\nTo protect against issues like this, we should always set `this.props` and `this.state` right before calling a lifecycle method, as if they were explicit arguments.",
